	* ircd/m_whois.c: Do not #include "whocmds.h".
	(MAX_WHOIS_USERS): Moved from whocmds.h.

	* ircd/parse.c: Do not #include "whocmds.h".

	* ircd/Makefile.in: Remove mention of whocmds.  Update depends.

